      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;certifications--training&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Certifications &amp;amp; Training&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#certifications--training&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;in-progress&#34;&gt;&#xA;  In Progress&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#in-progress&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner&lt;/strong&gt; — studying&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA)&lt;/strong&gt; — studying&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;planned&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Planned&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#planned&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Google Cloud Professional Cloud Architect&lt;/strong&gt; — relevant to my current GCP, ADK, and Terraform work&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Docker Certified Associate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;courses-completed&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Courses Completed&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#courses-completed&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Advanced Python Programming&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Beyond Advanced Python&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Kubernetes and Helm for Java Developers&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Deploying and Managing Microservices&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Spring Boot Development&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Deploying Charts with Helmfile&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;These courses and the certifications I&amp;rsquo;m working toward reflect my commitment to staying current with cloud computing, containerisation, DevOps, and AI engineering.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Projects</title>
      <link>https://williamomeara.cuchulainntech.ie/projects/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://williamomeara.cuchulainntech.ie/projects/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;projects&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Projects&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#projects&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A selection of products and tools I&amp;rsquo;ve designed and built — most under &lt;a href=&#34;https://cuchulainntech.ie&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Cú Chulainn Tech&lt;/a&gt;. Status tags reflect each project&amp;rsquo;s real state today.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;ai--developer-tooling&#34;&gt;&#xA;  AI &amp;amp; Developer Tooling&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#ai--developer-tooling&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;iam-legend&#34;&gt;&#xA;  iam-legend&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#iam-legend&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A GCP IAM toolbelt for AI agents and CI pipelines. It parses Terraform, ADK Python, and &lt;code&gt;gcloud&lt;/code&gt; scripts, recommends least-privilege roles using a set-cover algorithm over a catalog of 2,300+ roles and 13,000+ permissions, and posts AI-driven IAM reviews on pull requests to catch permission gaps before &lt;code&gt;terraform apply&lt;/code&gt; fails. Built for the &lt;strong&gt;Google for Startups AI Agents Challenge 2026&lt;/strong&gt;.&#xA;&lt;code&gt;Python · Gemini/Vertex AI · FastAPI · MCP / CLI / GitHub Action&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Open source · &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/williamomeara/iam-legend&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
