    <item>
      <title>Education</title>
      <link>https://williamomeara.cuchulainntech.ie/education/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Nov 2025 17:32:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://williamomeara.cuchulainntech.ie/education/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;education&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Education&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#education&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;bachelor-of-science-in-computer-science&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Bachelor of Science in Computer Science&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#bachelor-of-science-in-computer-science&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;University College Dublin, Ireland&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;em&gt;Final Year GPA: 3.8/4.2&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The UCD School of Computer Science has an established record in scholarship and research in this thriving sector.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;study-abroad-in-computer-science&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Study Abroad in Computer Science&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#study-abroad-in-computer-science&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;San Jose State University, USA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;em&gt;Year-long program&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Selected as one of five students—and the sole representative from computer science—for a year-long study abroad at San Jose State University. This experience enhanced my adaptability to new environments while providing invaluable opportunities to engage with a diverse, international student community.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Experience</title>
